query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS order_history (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  orderId INT NOT NULL,
  changeType ENUM('created', 'updated', 'imported', 'manual_edit', 'reimported') NOT NULL,
  changedBy INT,
  changedFields JSON,
  previousData JSON,
  newData JSON,
  source VARCHAR(100),
  notes TEXT,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX order_idx (orderId),
  INDEX change_type_idx (changeType),
  INDEX created_at_idx (createdAt)
);
